_sText:
Welcome to my first ever map! 

This map consists of 3 areas that divide the spawn points for you and your team mates to dish it out, old school style. I did my best with the structure and have included a reasonable attempt at lighting.

I did used 3kliksphilip's tutorials and he was a very credible teacher. There is one displacement usage in the map and it may look a bit ugly because I wanted it to be realistic and hide the *other* parts of the map. There is a player clip to prevent further complications such as falling off.

*UPDATE* 2011 18th of May

Due to a lack of training and usage of tutorials to create this map properly, there is a few glitches such as the missing textures. The map remains here because it is my first reasonable attempt at mapping. I am continuously trying to improve my structure, quality and positioning of player entities in my maps. 

I will continue to contribute with better quality contents that will definitely surpass the ludicrous excuse for a map.
